    {
      "heading": "Detailed description",
      "text": "The MikroTik nRayAIM-DH1 is a precision alignment and aiming accessory designed specifically for the Wireless Wire nRAY. This attachment allows you to mount a scope of your choice, enabling more accurate alignment and simplifying the installation process of your nRAY devices. With its robust and practical design, the nRayAIM-DH1 ensures precise antenna positioning, which is essential for achieving optimal signal quality and stable long-distance wireless connections. Whether you’re setting up a new point-to-point link or fine-tuning an existing installation, this accessory makes the alignment process faster, easier, and more efficient. Built with reliability and usability in mind, the nRayAIM-DH1 is an indispensable tool for professional network installers and anyone aiming for the best possible performance from their Wireless Wire nRAY system."
    }
